@node "Introduction" "Introduction"
 INTRODUCTION

     Atoms is a nice game where luck and ability are needed to win.

     This is the newest version of my most famous game: "Atoms"; I said
"my", but actually it isn't totally true since the idea is copied from a
similar game by Hewlett for ST.

     I hope to have improved that one and made a better game, also thanking
to the great power of Amiga!!: enjoy yourself playing it!
@endnode

