@node "AI Routines" "AI routines"
 ABOUT AI:

Atoms is a quite complex game, even if it seems to be easy to play.

Making good AI routines wasn't easy, also because they had to be not too
slow. It could sound incredible, but the Easy level can also win the Hard
one when playing one against the other and this is because luck can help
it!

I played quite a lot of time during the beta-tests and I can say the
computer players aren't so bad, even if they can be won. So, start playing
and look who's the best around!
@endnode

